headline: Carnival Corporation's 'Less Left Over' Strategy Beats Targets, Delivers Significant Food Waste Reduction Progress
summary: Carnival Corporation & plc (NYSE/LSE: CCL; NYSE: CUK), the world's largest cruise company, today announced it achieved a 44% reduction in unit food waste in 2024 compared to 2019 levels, surpassing its 2025 40% reduction target a full year ahead of schedule and is well on its way toward its 50% reduction goal set for 2030.
